  "title": "Sales Executive (5 days / Funeral Industry)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Facilitate project planning sessions and align efforts between internal teams and external stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Supervise project management tasks to ensure timely and efficient execution.</li>\n  <li>Create and update comprehensive project documentation to maintain accuracy and transparency.</li>\n  <li>Analyze project performance and identify areas for improvement.</li>\n  <li>Mitigate project risks by implementing proactive risk management strategies.</li>\n  <li>Enhance value generation in deal negotiations and transactions.</li>\n  <li>Design and optimize workflows and protocols for the new business division.</li>\n  <li>Assist leadership in assessing and pursuing tenders, projects, and strategic partnerships.</li>\n  <li>Cultivate and expand critical business relationships.</li>\n  <li>Design and launch new products/services as directed by the Group.</li>\n  <li>Oversee and grow promising business units and brands.</li>\n  <li>Deliver consistent progress reports to senior management.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
